# DarkShop – Dark Themed E-Commerce UI

A modern dark-themed product showcase layout designed using HTML and CSS.

## 📌 Features

- Dark UI design
- Responsive grid layout
- Product cards with hover effects
- Sale and New badges
- Styled search bar
- Rating display
- Call-to-action buttons

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- CSS Grid
- Hover transitions

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Open the HTML file in a web browser.
2. Hover over product cards to view animation effects.

## 🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice:
- Dark theme UI design
- CSS Grid layouts
- Card components
- Hover effects and transitions
- Modern e-commerce styling

